The paper discusses a trust management mechanism for SDN, which involves network infrastructure and security. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses security issues, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.SE (Software Engineering). The paper also discusses the scalability of the proposed mechanism, which could fall under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
